07:40.227 --> 07:42.663
Have you been drinking?
Are you on any medications?

07:42.763 --> 07:43.898
- No.
- Breathe.

07:43.998 --> 07:45.800
No, are you a doctor?

07:45.900 --> 07:46.767
No.

07:47.835 --> 07:49.170
