asked you all those questions.

07:51.472 --> 07:53.808
- I just want to go.
- Oh. Hey. Hey.

07:53.908 --> 07:55.076
I don't know my what...

07:55.176 --> 07:55.943
- I don't know...
- Hey, hey.

07:56.277 --> 07:57.278
- ...what is wrong with me.
- Look at me, look at me.

07:57.378 --> 07:59.814
