08:03.184 --> 08:04.819
Okay. Look at me. Look at me.

08:05.119 --> 08:06.320
Hey.

08:06.687 --> 08:08.222
Look at me.

08:08.989 --> 08:09.890
Just breathe.

08:12.893 --> 08:14.061
I'm here.

08:17.231 --> 08:18.933
