for no goddamn reason.

10:00.401 --> 10:01.402
How can you say that?

10:02.303 --> 10:04.104
How can you say that?

10:04.606 --> 10:08.142
Every night you accuse me,
and no matter what I say,

10:08.242 --> 10:10.144
